items.name: red-pump
items.description: A red pump model that is used for AR demonstrations

procedures.name: Show Me
procedures.description: Fully animated procedure with no touch interaction.

steps.title: Remove Front Panel
steps.text: Remove bolts retaining the outer case. Extract front panel.

steps.title: Extract Fan Assembly
steps.text: Decouple the fan assembly from the casing.

steps.title: Disassemble Fan
steps.text: Rotate the washer and rod assembly until the enclosure unlocks.  Carefully remove each part and place them in an accessible location for reassembly.

steps.title: Replace Worn Part
steps.text: Replace the worn fan with a replacement. Take note of the surrounding components and replace any other parts with visible wear.

steps.title: Reassemble Fan
steps.text: Reassemble the fan assembly in reverse order from your disassembly.  Parts are engineered to specifically align to prevent assembly error.

steps.title: Re-insert Fan Assembly
steps.text: Guide the fan assembly along the retaining rod to replace it into the case.

steps.title: Replace Outer Casing
steps.text: Replace the outer case and re-insert screws.
